title: Final Draft 9.0.7 OS X
description:
:: Year 2015, May 22th
:: Version 9.0.7
Developer :: Final Draft, Inc.
Platform :: Intel only
System requirements ::
OS X 10.7 or later

Interface languages :: Angliysky + Patch: Kataloncky, Danish, Dutch, English (UK), English (Canadian), French (Canada), French, German (Swiss), German, Italian, Norwegian, Portuguese (Brazilian), Portuguese (European ), Spanish, Swedish.
Medicine :: Present

Run Final Draft 9 Installer
Run the application in Demo mode and close the program
Copy the file Final Draft 9 of the image in the folder MacOS (right click on the application => Show Package Contents => Contents => MacOS)
Block all outgoing connections via LS or Hands Off!
disable auto-update

* The original language of the program is English, but the image includes a folder with other languages
